<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= subject %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
        .header { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #333; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .content p { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .details strong { display: inline-block; width: 150px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        .button:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><%= appName %> - New Phone Change Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello Admin,</p>
            <p>A user has requested to change their phone number. Please review the details below:</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>User Name:</strong> <%= user.name %></p>
                <p><strong>User Email:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
                <p><strong>Previous Phone:</strong> <%= user.currentPhone %></p>
                <p><strong>Requested New Phone:</strong> <%= user.newPhone %></p>
                <p><strong>Request Date:</strong> <%= user.requestedAt %></p>
            </div>

            <p>To manage this request, please log in to the admin panel:</p>
            <p><a href="<%= adminUrl %>/users/phone-changes" class="button">Go to Admin Panel</a></p>
            
            <p>Thank you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= year %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you received this email in error, please disregard it.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>